--- a/adae_prog.R
+++ b/adae_prog.R
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 1: ASTDY calculation is ASTDT - TRTSDT without the +1 offset, giving day 0 instead of day 1 for first dose day events
+Fix 1: ASTDY adds +1 offset
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 2: TRTEMFL uses ASTDT > TRTSDT (strictly greater) instead of >=, excluding same-day events
+Fix 2: TRTEMFL uses >= for inclusive comparison
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 3: TRTPN is assigned from TRT01AN (actual) instead of TRT01PN (planned)
+Fix 3: TRTPN from TRT01PN (planned numeric treatment)

Summary of fixes:
1. ASTDY adds +1 offset (astdy_offset)
2. TRTEMFL uses >= for inclusive comparison (trtemfl_comparison)
3. TRTPN from TRT01PN (planned numeric treatment) (trtpn_source)
